---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Emprendimiento y CEO">

	<section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-slate-50 to-slate-100">
		<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-15 pointer-events-none">
			<div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-violetaIA/25 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
			<div class="absolute -bottom-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-verdeEsm/20 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
			<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(#94a3b8_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:40px_40px]"></div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10 text-center">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-azulCorp mb-6 leading-tight">
				Vision, Tecnologia y <br />
				<span class="bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r font-black text-azulCorp">Emprendimiento</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-lg text-slate-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
				Impulsando innovaciones locales con vision internacional. Desarrollo de hardware y software orientados a la efectividad productiva.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-slate-950">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Impacto Tecnologico y Social</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
					Disminuyendo la brecha tecnologica regional mediante sistemas adaptables al sector residencial, comercial e industrial en la era de 5ta generacion.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
				<div class="p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-violetaIA mb-4">Desarrollo de Software</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						Estimula el proceso de aprendizaje mediante un organizador digital amigable. Cuenta con seleccion simple y comandos de voz para disminuir la saturacion neurologica o estres.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-3">
						<li class="flex items-start text-sm text-slate-400"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-violetaIA mt-1.5 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span> Rastreo, ubicacion y bloqueo en caso de robo o extravio.</li>
						<li class="flex items-start text-sm text-slate-400"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-violetaIA mt-1.5 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span> Intercambio de informacion modificable y actualizable.</li>
						<li class="flex items-start text-sm text-slate-400"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-violetaIA mt-1.5 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span> Simuladores para actividades organizacionales y gerenciales.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="relative rounded-[2.5rem] bg-slate-900 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center p-8 overflow-hidden group min-h-[300px]">
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-violetaIA/20 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
					<div class="text-center text-slate-500 z-10">
						<svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 opacity-50" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
						<span class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest px-4 block">Espacio: Capturas de la App (SMS, GPS, Gas)</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
				<div class="relative rounded-[2.5rem] bg-slate-900 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center p-8 overflow-hidden group min-h-[300px] order-2 md:order-1">
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tl from-verdeEsm/20 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
					<div class="text-center text-slate-500 z-10">
						<svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 opacity-50" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"/></svg>
						<span class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest px-4 block">Espacio: Foto Tarjeta Electronica / Just In</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors order-1 md:order-2">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-verdeEsm mb-4">Integracion de Hardware</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						La tarjeta electronica administra funciones preestablecidas en comandos simples. Emite sonidos, enciende luces y notifica alarmas al usuario final.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-3">
						<li class="flex items-start text-sm text-slate-400"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-verdeEsm mt-1.5 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span> Modulo GPS para posicionamiento y control de rango.</li>
						<li class="flex items-start text-sm text-slate-400"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-verdeEsm mt-1.5 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span> Sensores para humo, monoxido de carbono y gases toxicos.</li>
						<li class="flex items-start text-sm text-slate-400"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-verdeEsm mt-1.5 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span> Escalable para gestion tecnologica industrial.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 md:py-32">
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
			<div>
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-azulCorp mb-6">Riesgo y Sostenibilidad</h2>
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-azulCorp mb-6">Desde la Investigacion a la Empresa</h2>
				<span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-violetaIA uppercase bg-violetaIA/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6 inline-block">
					Universidad Emprendedora
				</span>
				<p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					Profesores y estudiantes de la Universidad del Zulia (LUZ), expusieron diversos proyectos innovadores durante las Decimas Jornadas: Universidad Emprendedora: Desde la Investigacion a la Empresa, Gestion del Conocimiento, Emprendimiento y Propiedad Intelectual.
				</p>
				<p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					Durante el evento, el profesor Andres Martinez presento el proyecto: <strong class="text-azulCorp">"Software y hardware para el monitoreo y memorizacion de actividades que permita la efectividad productiva"</strong>.
				</p>
				<p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
					Esta aplicacion esta disenada para diversos sectores, apoyando especialmente a quienes se les dificulta procesar y recordar gran cantidad de informacion simultanea, asi como a personas con impedimentos fisicos o de edad avanzada.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="relative group rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden bg-slate-100 aspect-[4/3] border border-slate-200 shadow-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
				<div class="text-center text-slate-600 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 z-10">
					<svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 opacity-50" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
					<span class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest px-4 block">Espacio: Foto del Evento LUZ</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 md:py-32">
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-azulCorp mb-4">Reconocimientos Profesionales</h2>
			<p class="text-slate-700">Certificaciones otorgadas por la presentacion de innovaciones tecnologicas y ponencias.</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
			<div class="relative group rounded-[2rem] bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm aspect-[4/3] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
				<div class="text-center text-slate-600">
					<svg class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-3 opacity-50" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
					<span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest block px-4">Certificado Decimas Jornadas</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="relative group rounded-[2rem] bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm aspect-[4/3] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
				<div class="text-center text-slate-600">
					<svg class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-3 opacity-50" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
					<span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest block px-4">Certificado IX Congreso Int.</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="relative group rounded-[2rem] bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm aspect-[4/3] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
				<div class="text-center text-slate-600">
					<svg class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-3 opacity-50" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
					<span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest block px-4">Certificado VIII Congreso Nacional</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="bg-slate-50 py-20 md:py-32 border-t border-slate-200">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
			
			<div>
				<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-azulCorp mb-8">Informacion de Contacto</h3>
				
				<div class="p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-white border border-slate-200 shadow-xl mb-10">
					<ul class="space-y-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
						<li class="flex items-center">
							<span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-verdeEsm/10 text-verdeEsm flex items-center justify-center mr-4"><svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg></span>
							<span class="text-base">Mensajeria: <span class="font-bold">+58 0424-626.26.36</span></span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-violetaIA/10 text-violetaIA flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg></span>
							<div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
								<a href="mailto:gerencia@1nnovacion.com" class="hover:underline font-medium">gerencia@1nnovacion.com</a>
								<a href="mailto:admin@1nnovacion.com" class="hover:underline font-medium">admin@1nnovacion.com</a>
								<a href="mailto:coordinacion@1nnovacion.com" class="hover:underline text-slate-600">coordinacion@1nnovacion.com</a>
								<a href="mailto:atencionalcliente@1nnovacion.com" class="hover:underline text-slate-600">atencionalcliente@1nnovacion.com</a>
							</div>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Metodos de Pago Autorizados</h4>
				<div class="flex gap-4 items-center">
					<div class="w-32 h-14 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-slate-600 font-bold shadow-sm hover:border-azulCorp transition-colors cursor-pointer">
						BANESCO
					</div>
					<div class="w-32 h-14 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-slate-600 font-bold shadow-sm hover:border-azulCorp transition-colors cursor-pointer">
						PAYPAL
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div>
				<div class="p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white border border-slate-200 shadow-2xl relative">
					<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-bl from-verdeEsm/10 to-transparent rounded-tr-[2.5rem]"></div>
					
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-azulCorp mb-2 relative z-10">Plantilla de Solicitud</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-8 relative z-10">Complete el formulario para informacion adicional o coordinaciones.</p>
					
					<form class="grid gap-5 relative z-10">
						<div>
							<label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Nombre Completo</label>
							<input type="text" placeholder="Ej. Andres Martinez" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3.5 text-sm focus:border-violetaIA focus:ring-1 focus:ring-violetaIA outline-none transition-all" />
						</div>
						<div>
							<label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Correo Electronico</label>
							<input type="email" placeholder="correo@ejemplo.com" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3.5 text-sm focus:border-violetaIA focus:ring-1 focus:ring-violetaIA outline-none transition-all" />
						</div>
						<div>
							<label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Mensaje / Requerimiento</label>
							<textarea rows="4" placeholder="Â¿En que podemos asistirle?" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3.5 text-sm focus:border-violetaIA focus:ring-1 focus:ring-violetaIA outline-none transition-all resize-none"></textarea>
						</div>
						<button type="button" class="mt-2 w-full rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-azulCorp to-slate-800 px-5 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-white hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-azulCorp/30 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
							ENVIAR SOLICITUD
						</button>
					</form>
				</div>
			</div>
			
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
